{id:"api-2014-races-dwarf",name:"Dwarf",content:[{id:"Title",content:"Dwarf"},{id:"StatGrid",content:[{title:"Speed",content:"25ft"},{title:"Size",content:"Medium"}]},{id:"MultiText",content:["***Age.***Dwarves mature at the same rate as humans, but they're considered young until they reach the age of 50. On average, they live about 350 years.","***Alignment.***Most dwarves are lawful, believing firmly in the benefits of a well-ordered society. They tend toward good as well, with a strong sense of fair play and a belief that everyone deserves to share in the benefits of a just order.","***Languages.***You can speak, read, and write Common and Dwarvish. Dwarvish is full of hard consonants and guttural sounds, and those characteristics spill over into whatever other language a dwarf might speak.","***Size.***Dwarves stand between 4 and 5 feet tall and average about 150 pounds. Your size is Medium."]},{id:"StatList",content:[{title:"Ability bonuses",content:["+2 CON"]},{title:"Languages",content:["Common","Dwarvish"]}]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"Traits"},{id:"LinkList",content:[{id:"@api-2014-traits-darkvision",content:""},{id:"@api-2014-traits-dwarven-resilience",content:""},{id:"@api-2014-traits-stonecunning",content:""},{id:"@api-2014-traits-dwarven-combat-training",content:""},{id:"@api-2014-traits-tool-proficiency",content:""}]},{id:"Subtitle",content:"Subraces"},{id:"LinkList",content:[{id:"@api-2014-subraces-hill-dwarf",content:""}]}]}